12:14.310 --> 12:16.920
- Where's my brother, where's Ray?

12:16.920 --> 12:19.550
- Doin' whatever Podunk
sheriffs do, I guess?

12:19.550 --> 12:20.883
What, whittling?

12:23.150 --> 12:23.983
- Really dude?

12:24.960 --> 12:27.007
You are not ready for primetime.

12:27.007 --> 12:29.250
(agents laughing)

12:29.250 --> 12:30.380
- That's why I joined the Bureau.

12:30.380 --> 12:31.213
- Mm-hmm.

12:33.030 --> 12:35.590
Your pal has got one hell of a story.

12:35.590 --> 12:37.240
- Yeah, he's got lots of stories.

12:38.750 --> 12:40.400
Not a whole lot of anything else.

12:41.580 --> 12:43.380
- You don't get along, do you?

12:43.380 --> 12:45.193
- Cain and Abel kind of thing, is it?

12:47.132 --> 12:49.720
- I don't know what he is anymore.

12:49.720 --> 12:50.553
- What?

12:51.660 --> 12:54.053
What do you mean by that, what he is?

12:55.460 --> 12:58.093
- Who, I said who.

12:59.080 --> 13:00.630
I don't know who he is anymore.

13:02.010 --> 13:03.550
Especially after what I saw.

13:03.550 --> 13:05.670
- Yeah, who's on first, what's on second,

13:05.670 --> 13:10.670
I don't know's on third,
after what exactly, Dale?

13:18.510 --> 13:19.343
- Nevermind.

13:20.390 --> 13:21.223
Just forget it.

13:24.549 --> 13:25.382
- Oh Dale.

13:27.260 --> 13:30.363
You know there's some things
one can not just forget.

13:32.510 --> 13:34.660
-  Ah shit, my back!

13:34.660 --> 13:36.410
- Alan, oh my god, I'm sorry!

13:36.410 --> 13:37.670
- What happened?

13:37.670 --> 13:38.620
-  She threw the dart into my back,

13:38.620 --> 13:39.453
that's what happened.

13:39.453 --> 13:40.814
- I mean, what happened to the lights?

13:40.814 --> 13:41.647
- Oh my god.

13:41.647 --> 13:43.490
- Can somebody go get
the first aid kid, Tanya?

13:43.490 --> 13:47.390
- Let me help, I should put
my nursing degree to some use.

13:47.390 --> 13:50.013
- I got it, I messed it up, I'll fix it.

13:50.013 --> 13:51.040
- You got my beer?

13:51.040 --> 13:52.207
- Yeah, I got it.

13:54.980 --> 13:55.830
- My brother will know what to--

13:55.830 --> 13:57.620
- Your brother will know what to what?

13:57.620 --> 14:00.310
- What to do when a fuse
blows in this shit-box

14:00.310 --> 14:01.933
your daddy was so proud of.

14:08.810 --> 14:12.610
- You just keep my father's
name out of your mouth.

14:12.610 --> 14:13.443
- Or what?

14:13.443 --> 14:16.180
- It's not polite to speak
ill of the dead, Carl.

14:16.180 --> 14:17.013
- And?

14:18.270 --> 14:20.720
I spent my whole life being polite.

14:20.720 --> 14:23.720
I spent my whole life livin'
by my daddy's good book.

14:23.720 --> 14:24.930
Where'd it get me?

14:24.930 --> 14:26.323
