15:25.430 --> 15:26.320
- Six years.

15:26.320 --> 15:27.153
- Six years.

15:27.153 --> 15:28.570
- Yeah, so they tell me.

15:28.570 --> 15:31.900
So you've told me, repeatedly.

15:31.900 --> 15:32.733
- Told you?

15:34.580 --> 15:36.420
What do you mean by that?

15:36.420 --> 15:38.450
- What do you want me to say?

15:38.450 --> 15:41.803
- Nothing big, just the truth.

15:42.830 --> 15:46.910
- No, that's the last
thing you wanna hear.

15:46.910 --> 15:48.530
- Try us.

15:48.530 --> 15:51.270
- And you can start with, why did you need

15:51.270 --> 15:53.793
someone to tell you how
long you've been gone for?

15:56.028 --> 15:57.940
(crickets chirping)

15:57.940 --> 15:59.540
