16:28.330 --> 16:29.510
- You shoulda charged it babe.

16:29.510 --> 16:32.560
- I did, like an hour ago.

16:32.560 --> 16:34.550
- Why don't you make
yourself useful, you call.

16:34.550 --> 16:35.840
-  Don't have one.

16:35.840 --> 16:37.400
