17:08.108 --> 17:10.858
(crickets chirp)

17:20.720 --> 17:21.920
- This is what it's come down to,

17:21.920 --> 17:23.586
the Campbells spreading
all over everything

17:23.586 --> 17:25.000
Dad built like some kind of mold?

17:25.000 --> 17:27.670
- It's done Joseph, it's time to move on.

17:27.670 --> 17:28.623
- To where?

17:30.140 --> 17:31.790
- I figured I would ask you that,

17:31.790 --> 17:33.683
you're the expert on movin' on.

17:34.590 --> 17:36.160
- That's not fair.

17:36.160 --> 17:39.350
- Joe, you left me here
alone when Dad was sick,

17:39.350 --> 17:41.480
what was I supposed to do?

17:41.480 --> 17:43.610
The Campbells were there, you weren't.

17:43.610 --> 17:46.110
- And now they've come
to collect, is that it?

17:46.110 --> 17:49.300
- You can't just show up after six years,

17:49.300 --> 17:50.500
refuse to tell anybody where you--

17:50.500 --> 17:51.333
- It's complicated.

17:51.333 --> 17:52.360
- It's not complicated!

17:52.360 --> 17:54.650
You pick up the phone, you
tell us you're still alive!

17:54.650 --> 17:57.963
We had a funeral for you
Joseph, we buried a suit.

17:59.060 --> 18:00.550
- But why them?

18:00.550 --> 18:03.493
They already own the whole goddamn town.

18:04.590 --> 18:07.053
(Joseph sighs)

18:07.053 --> 18:09.470
(clattering)

18:10.888 --> 18:14.721
