have done in my shoes?

18:17.790 --> 18:20.130
- I'm not saying I have the answer,

18:20.130 --> 18:21.830
but we both know this can't be it.

18:25.740 --> 18:28.273
- You know, you oughta save
the sermon for the Reverend.

18:32.288 --> 18:34.705
(clattering)

18:36.660 --> 18:37.493
Try it now.

18:43.340 --> 18:46.007
